reviewText: This is a tribal fusion performance dvd featuring Narah from the North EAst.  Beautiful dancer!

Don't buy this DVD. I tried to play it in my DVD player and got a disc error message and would not play.  I also tried to play it on my computer and not only did it not play, but also caused my computer to crash from a fatal error. I am out $25 bucks. Very dissapointed because Amazon does not offer refunds for opened Dvds.
